{"title":"解決固定導覽列與錨點的衝突","uid":"a4bc86905e91284a7270b344b882f194","slug":"solve-conflicts-with-navbar-and-anchor","date":"2022-08-15T13:46:00.000Z","updated":"2022-12-26T10:32:45.872Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/solve-conflicts-with-navbar-and-anchor.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>在我正在愁思應如何運用 CSS 方法解決固定導覽列與錨點的衝突，衝突是在於當錨點被導航後，會因為<strong>固定的導覽列懸浮於網頁的頂端，而看似造成滾動過度</strong>。</p>\n<p>當然，若是你把錨點設定於<strong>區塊元素</strong>，如 <code>&lt;div&gt;</code> 或者是一些<strong>語意化標示</strong>如 <code>&lt;section&gt;</code>，衝突效果並不顯著的，但是把其設定於標題，就另當別論了。</p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"解決方法\"><a href=\"#解決方法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"解決方法\"></a>解決方法</h1><p>幸好，世界上有如此的解決方法，這個方法是從 <a href=\"https://getpublii.com/blog/one-line-css-solution-to-prevent-anchor-links-from-scrolling-behind-a-sticky-header.html\" target=\"_blank\">publii</a> 內其中一個文章得到的，大家可以到那裏看看詳解。</p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">參考資料：publii</p>\n<p>Fortunately, we have a new, simple, one-line CSS solution: <code>scroll-margin-top</code> and <code>scroll-padding-top</code>.</p>\n</div>\n<p>這裏就給出解決固定導覽列令錨點導航至標題，而造成過度滾動的解決方法，關鍵是使用 <code>scroll-padding-top</code> 屬性。</p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">提示</p>\n<p><code>scroll-padding-top</code> 和 <code>scroll-margin-top</code> 的<strong>內距和邊界都不會影響網頁的佈局</strong>，只會影響滾動時的佈局。</p>\n</div>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><div class=\"caption\"><span>index.html</span></div><code class=\"language-markup\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\n&lt;html&gt;\n&lt;head&gt;\n    &lt;link rel&#x3D;&quot;stylesheet&quot; href&#x3D;&quot;style.css&quot;&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;head&gt;\n&lt;body&gt;\n    &lt;a href&#x3D;&quot;#test&quot;&gt;Click me&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;\n    &lt;h2 id&#x3D;&quot;test&quot;&gt;Heading&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;body&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;html&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><div class=\"caption\"><span>style.css</span></div><code class=\"language-css\">html, h2 &#123;\n    scroll-padding-top: 4rem;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<p>簡單快捷的一篇文章，是給自己記錄這個絕妙方法摘錄筆記，並希望以上方法能有幫助。</p>\n","text":"在我正在愁思應如何運用 CSS 方法解決固定導覽列與錨點的衝突，衝突是在於當錨點被導航後，會因為固定的導覽列懸浮於網頁的頂端，而看似造成滾動過度。 當然，若是你把錨點設定於區塊元素，如 &lt;div&gt; 或者是一些語意化標示如 &lt;section&gt;，衝突效果並不顯...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":922,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"網頁開發","slug":"網頁開發","count":7,"path":"api/categories/網頁開發.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"CSS","slug":"CSS","count":4,"path":"api/tags/CSS.json"},{"name":"HTML","slug":"HTML","count":3,"path":"api/tags/HTML.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">解決方法</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"BlueWhaleYT","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://i.ibb.co/zRvn96K/20210718-233824.jpg","link":"/","description":"Everything is possible, as long as you are powerful.","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"HTML 文件的跳脫字元","uid":"3cd6dfa1f1d694a9161229865a57df9f","slug":"html-escape-character","date":"2022-08-19T13:36:00.000Z","updated":"2022-12-25T14:20:23.070Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/html-escape-character.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"在你編寫 HTML 文件時，你經常所使用的 &lt; 和 &gt; 字符，想必對你並不陌生。 可是，你有沒有想過，HTML 看重的以上那些字符